{"tid":2450094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"62歲男遮打集會襲警判囚 上訴提新證據 押下月中裁決","createTime":"2021-03-17T06:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T21:51:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2047095dede8eaaee2399b1ed2bcc07268fa02","tid":2450094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"去年1月19日警方驅散在遮打花園的集會期間，六旬家庭司機擅自走出馬路並出拳攻擊一名制服他的速龍小隊成員，去年7月經審訊後被裁定襲警罪成，判監1個月。被告不服定罪及判刑提出上訴，其代表大狀今在高等法院透露，上訴人在等候上訴期間找到新的影片證據，可證明他當日不僅沒有刻意襲警，更遭警員「叉頸」。惟陳慶偉法官指出，辯方在案件審訊時乃稱被告遭警方揮棍毆打，「你唔可以嗰陣時話揮動警棍，今日先話叉頸㗎嘛」，並認為事發當日的集會雖然有不反對通知書，「但後嚟差人反對啊嘛，因為亂晒龍啊嘛」，故判刑應以整天發生的事作考慮。案件押後至下月15日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n代表大狀謝志浩指出，雖然新證據在案件審結後才出現，但並非辯方刻意收起，否則這是違反常理。謝續指，新的影片能展現一切真相，反映上訴人無出拳腳攻擊，若他真的有使用過「武力」都只是因被叉頸所致，故裁判官稱兩名控方證人誠實可靠的裁定，並站不住腳。謝又指出，上訴人在遭到警員猛烈制服下才會受傷，並且頭破血流，警員作供時形容上訴人流出來的血為「紅色液體」，是牽強的狡辯。<br />\n<br />\n惟答辯方律政司認為，上訴人在去年7月31日被定罪，他的兒子翌日便馬上找到新證據的源頭，可見只要他們在開審前盡其所能便能找到影片，而非定罪後才補救，否則只是浪費法庭時間，故法庭不應批准上訴人在上訴階段才呈上新影片。<br />\n<br />\n答辯方亦不認同影片削弱了警員的證供，反而證明了證員並無使用警棍，而是用手撘住上訴人膊頭，卻遭他撥開及推撞，與他們的作供大致肳合。另外，答辯方認為辯方在審訊時，僅向警員展示上訴人受傷的相片，他如何判斷其頭上的液體純屬他個人觀感，稱為「紅色液體」不屬狡辯。<br />\n<br />\n至於刑期上訴方面，謝指出案發的背景為一個合法的集會，嚴重性較低，故判監一個月屬過重；惟答辯方認為當天集會出現非常大規模示威，事發時警方正在清場，上訴人擅自走出馬路會影響驅散行動，反問：「呢個背景可唔可以話係輕微嘅襲警背景？」。"},{"pid":"6abc0301013cda9a8781c4b4f4cddaab3ca3eab2","tid":2450094,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66b61a4081018d39a901655fe6357386b98ad6d","tid":2450094,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caca831a0548b2627231159c4fef878702079643","tid":2450094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6abc0301013cda9a8781c4b4f4cddaab3ca3eab2","tid":2450094,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810e4e81eea34e6c9a851c3ca14f172786e11e27","tid":2450094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c66b61a4081018d39a901655fe6357386b98ad6d","tid":2450094,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109f051bf02253726201fdcdd48c7a06b2ed9c5a","tid":2450094,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"見到隻狗官名就知結果"},{"pid":"3126dfe47bc8693732c6ce7874c7a70b54bd5993","tid":2450094,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caca831a0548b2627231159c4fef878702079643","tid":2450094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6abc0301013cda9a8781c4b4f4cddaab3ca3eab2","tid":2450094,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b696b073bb16a5f288f6ffd7d0597cd6bcdb30f3","tid":2450094,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eef6f3ab665e8c3f4cb5fdce3c8cdc470b3710d","tid":2450094,"uid":190333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"你老味話明新證據<br />\n同之審果時有出入有幾奇"},{"pid":"1ce18d16111db51196d715a4858ff15c71c711ba","tid":2450094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"民間集會團隊去年1月在中環舉行「天下制裁」集會，中途遭警方腰斬，其間六旬司機被指襲擊速龍警員，遭多名警員制服拘捕，頭破血流，同年8月他被裁定襲警罪成，判監一個月。司機今於高等法院就定罪和判刑提出上訴，指找到新證據，可證當日出庭作供的兩名警員「表面信誓旦旦，其實並非實情」，上訴人非但沒有襲警，反遭警員叉頸，要求法官准許呈遞新證據。惟法官陳慶偉指，案發日中環發生的情況「亂晒籠」，屬本案背景，法庭必須考慮，將案押後下月15日宣判上訴結果。<br />\n<br />\n代表大狀謝志浩指出，原審裁判官香淑嫻裁決時指兩名作供警員完全沒有仗用任何武力，遑論過份武力，惟上訴人找到新證據，包括影片與照片，對法庭定奪真相極具作用，要求法庭接納上訴方呈遞作新證據；他解釋是在審訊完結後才發現新證據，若一早找到「仲邊有人會面對刑事審訊，都將極度明顯對自己有利嘅證據收起唔用?」<br />\n<br />\n他指，兩名作供的警員作供聲稱沒有採用武力，但其實防暴驅趕在場人士後，上訴人因遭警員叉頸，於是出於自然反應用手撥開，惟警員卻一湧而上，將上訴人按在地上，並有警員以胡椒噴劑的罐身擊打其頭部，致血流披面。大狀指，從新影片可見，「警方完全沒有動粗」的說法與事實不符；警員將上訴人流血形容為「紅色液體」，更是牽強。<br />\n<br />\n大律師稱，警員在庭上作供信誓旦旦，但長3分20多秒的片段顯示的，才是反映當時事實，更謂若裁判官有觀看片段，定必不會形容兩名警員誠實可靠，新證據絕對可打擊定罪的安穩性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/FFS6LBFJMFC3JDPJSNGMAKGHXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FFFS6LBFJMFC3JDPJSNGMAKGHXM%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=91b4b8ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FFFS6LBFJMFC3JDPJSNGMAKGHXM%2F&h=960f198e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/FFS6LBFJMFC3JDPJSNGMAKGHXM/</a>"},{"pid":"95b4fa7a8c73365bbc69f4656fe382d8b3aed447","tid":2450094,"uid":337826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"極速搵到新證據都係錯<br />\n真係你玩埋我個份"},{"pid":"b326362af56db0dd6b42fa8d37958914e51fbb99","tid":2450094,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd3dd54a90fff8ed9b048cf25bdca2cd2ab7cb7","tid":2450094,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"有片都無真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DOJ好波"},{"pid":"42bcfe9e73ebead0caee85d8b3fd5413e40d1220","tid":2450094,"uid":240036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"好大嘅官威，幫到咁出面不如咪接納新證據啦笨"},{"pid":"f57485d99554a021b532832bc089b27c1d6ae073","tid":2450094,"uid":190333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4dd3dd54a90fff8ed9b048cf25bdca2cd2ab7cb7","tid":2450094,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"有片都無真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DOJ好波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"陳官：當時亂哂籠，所以可以亂砌人生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e1d3da1f7047f3191f8aadee64bbc8aba6cce6","tid":2450094,"uid":95577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5eef6f3ab665e8c3f4cb5fdce3c8cdc470b3710d","tid":2450094,"uid":190333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"你老味話明新證據<br />\n同之審果時有出入有幾奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"上訴係有規定唔可以俾新證據<br />\n如果要攞出嚟要先有法官批准<br />\n依加個官係話，你原審果時話俾人扑，依加先話俾人叉頸<br />\n咁係不一致"},{"pid":"126b42a87f6b3bfd8e6cdfd8389069c9428c42dc","tid":2450094,"uid":95577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42bcfe9e73ebead0caee85d8b3fd5413e40d1220","tid":2450094,"uid":240036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"好大嘅官威，幫到咁出面不如咪接納新證據啦笨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"其實法例規定<br />\n攞新證據果個要說服法庭點解要接納<br />\n唔接納係正常<br />\n個個上訴都話有新證據<br />\n一單官司打到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dc1bc49373d64a30852d1d75711cb815477435","tid":2450094,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"手足係咪保釋外出緊"},{"pid":"e5c924932c7b910728e6f7fcfb458a54435e62c6","tid":2450094,"uid":313162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"903e2d375217bd60210122732aeddb9a704bafb8","tid":2450094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3dc1bc49373d64a30852d1d75711cb815477435","tid":2450094,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"手足係咪保釋外出緊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"c75db97689b4ff88fda33ae2ab80a4f48ec1627a","tid":2450094,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"903e2d375217bd60210122732aeddb9a704bafb8","tid":2450094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"